&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking for a new opportunity within our new Extended Primary care services?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you passionate about ensuring people have the right choices for healthcare at the right time?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for… &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Candidates with a professional yet caring and flexible approach. As an administrator you will be part of a fantastic team and services managing peoples presenting needs within the City in extended and out of hours care. We share a goal and commitment to making a difference. You will contribute to leading the smooth running of our urgent care portfolio of services and enabling the best outcomes for people.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The EPIC 24 services are staffed using a bank of workers engaged on contract for services. We are currently looking to expand our bank of Administrators, if you would like further information or to put forward your expression of interest contact Sue Turner; susan.turner15@nhs.net 07412 777845.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
